
OMNÍPOTENS sempitérne Deus, qui hujus diéi venerándam sanctámque lætítiam in beáti Apóstoli tui Bartholomæi festivitáte tribuísti: da Ecclésiæ tuæ, quæsumus; et amáre quod crédidit, et prædicáre quod dócuit. Per Dóminum.
O ALMIGHTY, eternal God, who hast given the solemn and holy joy of thhis day for the feast of thy blessed Apostle Bartholomew; grant unto thy Church, we beseech thee, both to love what he believed and to preach what he taught. Through our Lord.
